# Umrechnungen

**x Bit = x Byte * 8**
**x Byte = x Bit / 8**
#### in Binary
![[Screenshot 2023-09-09 at 06.58.58 1.png |150]]
#### in Decimal
![[Screenshot 2023-09-09 at 06.58.48.png |150]]
#### XiB -> XB
1. **XiB -> Byte**
*x XiB * 1024<sup>x</sup>= x Byte*
50 MiB * 1024^2 =  52.428.800 Byte
2. Byte -> XB
*x Byte /  (1000<sup>x</sup>)*
52.428.800 Byte / (1000<sup>2</sup>)  = 52,4288 MB
#### XB -> XiB
1. **XB -> Byte**
*x XB * 1000<sup>x</sup>= x Byte*
50 MB * 1000^2 =  50.000.000 Byte
2. **Byte -> XiB**
*x Byte /  (1024<sup>x</sup>)*
50.000.000 Byte (1024<sup>x</sup>) â‰ˆ 47.68MiB

